Dialogue: 0,00:04:39.21,00:04:41.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾏﾘ)《フッ やっぱり｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:44.63,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Como pensaba, reserva el chakra\Npara enfrentarse a Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:41.21,00:04:45.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,チャクラは我愛羅のために取っておこうってわけか》
